      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This used car is in fair condition. The exterior has visible scratches and some minor dents, and the paint shows fading in certain areas. The interior has noticeable wear on the seats and surfaces, though it remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs but may benefit from some maintenance attention in the near term. Suitable for a buyer willing to accept cosmetic imperfections and potential minor repairs.",
